The lovely folk at @kassa sent me their chalkboard markers and chalkboard decal to try out, so I did! Verdict: this stuff is really good. The chalkboard decal is basically a roll of contact, so you can stick it to anything or cut it to any shape - good alternative to blackboard paint.  I'm using the liquid chalk pens on it here, but regular chalk also works really well. (I prefer liquid chalk for wedding signage because it's more vivid and a bit easier to work with.)
.
This sign is the chalkboard decal over a glass frame insert - plus i painted the frame gold. You know I like a bit of bling 😘
